@startuml SecHack365-Fans_PyJailBreak

package "Frontend" {
  [React Components] as RC
  [Redux Store] as RS
  [Next.js Pages] as NP
}

package "Backend" {
  [API Server] as API
}

cloud "Deployment" {
  [GitHub Pages] as GP
}

node "Target Environment" {
  [Vulnerable Server] as VS
}

RC --> RS : uses
NP --> RC : renders
NP --> RS : accesses state

Frontend --> API : sends requests
API --> VS : scans

Frontend --> GP : deploys to

@enduml